name: Selena - Witch of Bone Valley #1
description:
Collectible digital cards from one of my character from TRIBES project that I worked on since 2015.


Selena - Witch of The Bone Valley

“She's malicious, determined and frank. This is to be expected from somebody with her tormented past.

She was born and grew up in a great family in a normal port, she lived comfortably until she was about 5 years old, but at that point everything changed.

She lost her sister in a robbery gone wrong and was now alone and forgotten. Alongside a brother she had to survive in a pitiless world. But with her cunning and skills, she managed to escape hell and go beyond expectations. This has turned her into the woman she is today."
